// MatisseOptions.lara (library) - Utility aspects for setting MATISSE options //// The aspects on this file can be used by adding the line "import MatisseOptions;" at the beginning of an aspect// // Define if get/set functions for dynamic arrays should be inlined.// Inlined get/set functions provide faster C code, but do not do memory integrity checks.//// INPUTS:// - boolean_value: if true, get/set functions to dynamic matrices will be inlinedaspectdef allow_dynamic_allocation	input boolean_value end	select app end	apply		def allow_dynamic_allocation = boolean_value;	endend